      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I am absolutely thrilled to be listing this beauty! It is in truly flawless condition\u2014honestly, it still looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor. Not a single scratch or dent to be found, and it drives like a dream. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and I\u2019m only selling because I\u2019m looking to downsize. I know I\u2019m still building my reputation here, so I\u2019ve priced it to move quickly! Come take a look, you definitely won't be disappointed! \u2728",
