    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This investment-grade E46 M3 showcases the pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering with its S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring six individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Double VANOS variable valve timing. The drivetrain is anchored by a crisp Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec M-Variable limited-slip differential. Chassis integrity is paramount; this example has undergone proactive subframe reinforcement and retains its original suspension geometry with flawless bushings. The exterior displays factory-original paint depth and clarity, while the interior remains in a preserved state with no bolster wear on the Nappa leather. Every mechanical component, from the cooling system to the rod bearings, has been maintained to a rigorous standard, ensuring peak performance and reliability for the most discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 46500.0,
